---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SmartImage from '../components/SmartImage.astro';
import { IMAGES } from '../data/images';
---

<BaseLayout
  theme="story"
  title="About Blackburn Realty Group | Our Story"
  description="How Blackburn Realty Group became Florida's international real estate team — and why we operate the way we do."
>

<div class="breadcrumb">
  <div class="breadcrumb-inner">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
    <a href="/about/">About</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
    <span>Our Story</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ARRIVAL HERO — golden-hour, full-bleed, the room you walk into -->
<section class="story-hero" style={`--hero-img: url('${IMAGES.aboutHero.src}')`}>
  <div class="story-hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="story-hero-inner reveal">
    <p class="story-eyebrow">Our Story</p>
    <h1 class="story-hero-title">Florida's <em>front door</em><br/>to the world.</h1>
    <p class="story-hero-sub">Buying a home in a foreign country should never feel foreign. We meet you in your language, in your culture — with the standards of the largest independent brokerage in the state.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="story-hero-scroll">
    <span>Step inside</span>
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THE STORY — text and image woven together -->
<section class="story-body">
  <div class="story-lead reveal">
    <p>Olga Blackburn did not set out to build the most internationally diverse real estate team in Florida. She set out to solve a problem she lived herself.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="story-split">
    <div class="story-split-text reveal">
      <p>When Olga arrived in South Florida years ago, she discovered something the industry was quietly ignoring: international buyers were being handed off, overlooked, or talked down to because of the language they spoke. Buyers from Madrid, Lagos, Seoul, São Paulo, and Tel Aviv were spending millions on Florida property — and being treated like an inconvenience.</p>
      <p>She knew it could be done differently. So she started building.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="story-split-img reveal">
      <SmartImage image={IMAGES.aboutStory1} class="split-photo" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="story-full reveal">
    <p>She partnered with The Keyes Company — Florida's #1 independent brokerage, with 60+ offices and 4,000+ agents serving the state since 1926 — and created a division built around one mission: every buyer is served by an agent who speaks their language natively, understands their culture intimately, and is held to the highest standards of professional service in the state.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="story-quote reveal">
    <p class="story-quote-text">We do not translate the experience. We give the experience in your language from the very first conversation.</p>
    <p class="story-quote-attr">Olga Blackburn · Founder</p>
  </div>

  <div class="story-split story-split-rev">
    <div class="story-split-text reveal">
      <p>Today, Blackburn Realty Group represents 50 languages across 50 countries — one female and one male agent for each. Spanish from Madrid and Mexico City. Mandarin from Beijing and Taipei. Portuguese from Lisbon and Rio. Russian, Arabic, Korean, Hindi, Yoruba, Yiddish, Haitian Creole, and forty-three more. Every agent vetted, trained, and supported by the infrastructure of the largest independent brokerage in Florida.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="story-split-img reveal">
      <SmartImage image={IMAGES.aboutStory2} class="split-photo" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="story-full reveal">
    <p>And every agent, every transaction, every closing — backed by Stairway Mortgage for financing, by The Keyes Company for resources, and by Olga's personal standard of service that built the company in the first place.</p>
    <p class="story-close">This is what Florida should feel like to a buyer arriving from anywhere in the world. This is what we built.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THREE PILLARS — now with warmth and a hairline of colour -->
<section class="pillars">
  <div class="pillar reveal">
    <div class="pillar-num">01</div>
    <h3 class="pillar-title">Native Language</h3>
    <p class="pillar-text">Not translated. Native. Every agent grew up speaking the language of the clients they serve, and understands the cultural context that no app can translate.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pillar reveal">
    <div class="pillar-num">02</div>
    <h3 class="pillar-title">One Standard</h3>
    <p class="pillar-text">Whether you are buying a $300,000 condo or a $30 million waterfront estate, you receive the same level of service. The Keyes standard. The Blackburn standard. Always.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pillar reveal">
    <div class="pillar-num">03</div>
    <h3 class="pillar-title">One Team</h3>
    <p class="pillar-text">Your agent handles real estate. Stairway Mortgage handles financing. The Keyes infrastructure handles everything else. One point of contact. One trusted relationship.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INVITATION — warm close, image-backed -->
<section class="story-invite" style={`--invite-img: url('${IMAGES.aboutInvite.src}')`}>
  <div class="story-invite-veil"></div>
  <div class="story-invite-inner reveal">
    <p class="story-invite-eyebrow">Welcome to Florida</p>
    <h2 class="story-invite-title">Find your agent. <em>Start your journey.</em></h2>
    <p class="story-invite-body">Choose your language. Meet your agent. From this point forward, you are not alone in this market.</p>
    <div class="story-invite-btns">
      <a href="/ladies/" class="btn-ladies">Meet the Ladies</a>
      <a href="/guys/" class="btn-guys">Meet the Guys</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="mobile-sticky">
  <a href="/ladies/" class="mobile-sticky-btn">Find My Agent</a>
  <a href="/tools/preapproval/" class="mobile-sticky-btn">Get Pre-Approved</a>
  <a href="/tools/homevalue/" class="mobile-sticky-btn">Home Value</a>
</div>

<script is:inline>
  // Scroll-reveal — the room comes to life as you move through it.
  (function () {
    const els = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
    if (!('IntersectionObserver' in window)) {
      els.forEach(function (e) { e.classList.add('is-in'); });
      return;
    }
    const io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
      entries.forEach(function (entry) {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('is-in');
          io.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.12, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' });
    els.forEach(function (e) { io.observe(e); });
  })();
</script>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ─────────── ARRIVAL HERO ─────────── */
  .story-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 88vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 120px 32px 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(6,6,6,0.55) 0%, rgba(6,6,6,0.78) 55%, var(--black) 100%),
      var(--hero-img) center 30% / cover no-repeat;
  }
  /* warm amber glow bleeding up from the floor of the room */
  .story-hero-glow {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%; bottom: -30%;
    width: 120%; height: 60%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(var(--theme-rgb), 0.22), transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .story-hero-inner { position: relative; max-width: 900px; }
  .story-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.44em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--theme); margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .story-hero-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.2rem);
    line-height: 0.98; letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .story-hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
  .story-hero-sub {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.4vw, 1.6rem);
    color: var(--silver); line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .story-hero-scroll {
    position: absolute; bottom: 34px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .story-hero-scroll span {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.34em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--silver-dark);
  }
  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px; height: 46px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--theme), transparent);
    animation: scrollpulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes scrollpulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.35; transform: scaleY(0.7); }
    50% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleY(1); }
  }

  /* ─────────── STORY BODY ─────────── */
  .story-body { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 90px 52px 40px; }
  .story-lead { max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto 64px; text-align: center; }
  .story-lead p {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    line-height: 1.5; color: var(--silver-light);
  }
  .story-full { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto 64px; }
  .story-full p {
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300; font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 2; color: var(--silver-mid); margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .story-close {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif !important;
    font-style: italic; font-size: 1.5rem !important;
    color: var(--white) !important; line-height: 1.5 !important;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .story-split {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px; align-items: center;
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 72px;
  }
  .story-split-rev .story-split-img { order: -1; }
  .story-split-text p {
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300; font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 2; color: var(--silver-mid); margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .story-split-img {
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--theme-rgb), 0.18);
    min-height: 340px;
  }
  .story-split-img::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, transparent 55%, rgba(var(--theme-rgb), 0.16));
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .story-split-img :global(.smart-img) { height: 100%; }
  .story-split-img :global(.smart-img img) {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 340px;
    object-fit: cover; object-position: center 32%; display: block;
    filter: saturate(1.02) contrast(1.02);
    transition: transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.2,0.7,0.2,1);
  }
  .story-split-img:hover :global(.smart-img img) { transform: scale(1.05); }

  /* ─────────── PULL QUOTE ─────────── */
  .story-quote {
    max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto 80px;
    text-align: center; padding: 48px 40px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .story-quote::before {
    content: '"';
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 7rem; line-height: 0;
    color: rgba(var(--theme-rgb), 0.28);
    position: absolute; top: 46px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
  .story-quote-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.4vw, 2.3rem);
    line-height: 1.4; color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 22px; position: relative;
  }
  .story-quote-attr {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.34em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--theme);
  }

  /* ─────────── PILLARS ─────────── */
  .pillars {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 52px 100px;
  }
  .pillar {
    padding: 48px 34px; background: var(--near-black);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-top: 2px solid rgba(var(--theme-rgb), 0.5);
    text-align: center; transition: transform 0.4s, border-color 0.4s, background 0.4s;
  }
  .pillar:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    border-top-color: var(--theme);
    background: #101010;
  }
  .pillar-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300; font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--theme); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .pillar-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .pillar-text {
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300; font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--silver-dark); line-height: 1.85;
  }

  /* ─────────── INVITATION ─────────── */
  .story-invite {
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    padding: 130px 32px; text-align: center;
    /* jim-olga-pool-1.jpg: both stand full-length, faces high in the portrait,
       so bias the crop upward from 40% to keep both faces in the banner. */
    background: var(--invite-img) center 28% / cover no-repeat fixed;
  }
  .story-invite-veil {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--black) 0%, rgba(6,6,6,0.72) 40%, rgba(6,6,6,0.86) 100%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 120%, rgba(var(--theme-rgb),0.24), transparent 60%);
  }
  .story-invite-inner { position: relative; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .story-invite-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--theme); margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .story-invite-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
    line-height: 1.05; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .story-invite-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
  .story-invite-body {
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300; font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8; color: var(--silver);
    max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }
  .story-invite-btns { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-ladies, .btn-guys {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 16px 34px; border: 1px solid;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .btn-ladies { color: #f72585; border-color: #f72585; }
  .btn-ladies:hover { background: #f72585; color: var(--black); box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(247,37,133,0.4); }
  .btn-guys { color: #00d4b8; border-color: #00d4b8; }
  .btn-guys:hover { background: #00d4b8; color: var(--black); box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,212,184,0.4); }

  /* ─────────── SCROLL REVEAL ─────────── */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px);
    transition: opacity 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.2,0.7,0.2,1), transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.2,0.7,0.2,1);
  }
  .reveal.is-in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; transition: none; }
    .scroll-line { animation: none; }
  }

  /* ─────────── MOBILE ─────────── */
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .story-hero { min-height: 82vh; padding: 100px 22px 70px; background-attachment: scroll; }
    .story-body { padding: 60px 22px 20px; }
    .story-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .story-split-rev .story-split-img { order: 0; }
    .story-split-img img { min-height: 260px; }
    .pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 30px 22px 70px; gap: 16px; }
    .story-invite { padding: 90px 22px; background-attachment: scroll; }
  }
</style>
